description: David Icke - Infinite Love Is the Only Truth - Everything Else Is Illusion (pdf) - roflcopter2110 https://extraimage.net/images/2017/12/18/e9618b81c196b59f65f15051b3d6d45c.jpg Genre: Ancient & Controversial Knowledge, New Thought Publisher: David Icke Books Language: English ISBN-10: 0953881067 ISBN-13: 978-0953881062 Format: PDF A book that claims with such clarity that 'physical' reality is merely an illusion that only exists in our brain. Fantastic? Sure it is. But David Icke's idea, presented in a way that everyone can understand, is a life-changing exposure of both the illusion we believe to be 'real' and the way this illusion is generated and manipulated to imprison us in a false reality. Icke says we 'live' in a 'holographic internet' in that our brains are connected to a central 'computer' that feeds us the same collective reality that we decode from waveforms and electrical signals into the holographic 3D 'world' that we all think we see
